{"id":747514,"title":"02｜简洁的作用与误区","content":"","comments":[{"had_liked":false,"id":388306,"user_name":"精思入神","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1035038,"ip_address":"上海","ucode":"D5F47DD3C7530A","user_header":"http://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/Q0j4TwGTfTJUzv6S9wroyaa2CANjhHJcwRwNESncu4lfWTtdkMh3viaVCgEg5vMXFJ4Ne4SaDtLNd9dvkUrFqPg/132","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1709856032,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":141395,"content":"您好，您的认知很正确，加油，加油。","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"编辑","uid":2467716,"ctime":1709962701,"ip_address":"浙江","comment_id":388306,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":2,"product_id":100670901,"comment_content":"程序员其实天天都在写作，代码就是一种，要将代码当成文档写，提升可阅读性，当然包括注视在内，注释就是最紧密的技术文档，不容易变质掉队的文档。除了代码之外的技术文档，也是需要写作技巧，但大部分是硬文档，比较套路，如果能善于写作，将人文素养体现一点，立马会大放异彩。技术文档之外需要与人交流，这是事业扩大必须，表达与沟通非常重要，写作是关键工具。其实更重要的是，写作的习惯是锻炼思考力的日常修炼","like_count":0,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":2467716,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/25/a7/84/0e1403ac.jpg","nickname":"圆明居士胤禛","note":"","ucode":"C66DE217C0D604","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":638812,"discussion_content":"您好，您的认知很正确，加油，加油。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1709962701,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":"浙江","group_id":0},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2,\"source\":0}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":387019,"user_name":"罗耀龙@坐忘","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1917663,"ip_address":"广东","ucode":"3CEA258DE7F3C7","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/1d/42/df/a034455d.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1706170612,"is_pvip":true,"replies":[{"id":141430,"content":"您理解得很到位","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"编辑","uid":2467716,"ctime":1710145084,"ip_address":"浙江","comment_id":387019,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":4,"race_medal":2,"score":2,"product_id":100670901,"comment_content":"茶艺师学编程\n\n先说结论，出书要完成其【表达】所要达成的目的，而简洁仅仅是服务于这个目的。\n像《道德经》，精简到这种程度.......是的，当时的人都是这么说话的，记载的人也落个轻松，而且不用那么费劲刻竹简，当时的人都这么看......对于那个时空的人来说，这样就够了。\n到了现在，像《规模》，他考虑的是“我说的，我发布的研究成果，能让多少一般读者看懂？”，因此他慢慢说细细说。比如《人类简史》干的更绝，他会针对中国读者把故事素材换成中国的经典故事。\n\n就我自己来说，自己也在写一些技术型的公众号文。\n我在一些问题上磕磕碰碰，我也希望别人不要在这问题上踩坑，因此我写得也会啰嗦一点。\n如果我自己的水平上去了，也许也会默认读者已经懂了，到时就不会写的那么细节了。","like_count":0,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":2467716,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/25/a7/84/0e1403ac.jpg","nickname":"圆明居士胤禛","note":"","ucode":"C66DE217C0D604","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":638966,"discussion_content":"您理解得很到位","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1710145084,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":"浙江","group_id":0},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2,\"source\":0}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]},{"author":{"id":2467716,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/25/a7/84/0e1403ac.jpg","nickname":"圆明居士胤禛","note":"","ucode":"C66DE217C0D604","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":636468,"discussion_content":"了解反面，对月球的认识是不足的。写作的简和繁就需要根据它要服务的内容的对立模式而产生对应的模式，所以采用简或者繁，完全取决于内容是不是要求必须简或者繁。那么，功夫还是在识别内容如何才能打成目标上下功夫。而它们的转换，就在于场景，同样的内容，编辑成短视频文案就必须简洁，编辑成针对某些特定人群的书，则可能需要繁复。这就是相同内容的转换逻辑。然而，事实并非如此简单，转换的条件会有很多，就算是在同一本书里，也存在这种转换。\n还有，没有繁哪里有简洁？没有简洁哪会有繁复？所以，如果了解了繁复的原因和形式，也就能够通过某种方法思考到简洁的写法。相反的，知道了简洁的写法，也能够很快学会繁复的写法。","likes_number":1,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1706175099,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":"山东","group_id":0},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]},{"author":{"id":2467716,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/25/a7/84/0e1403ac.jpg","nickname":"圆明居士胤禛","note":"","ucode":"C66DE217C0D604","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":636463,"discussion_content":"我不反对简洁，反对的是为了简洁而简洁。有时，根据要达到的目的，繁复也是一种简洁。只要能到读者深刻理解的目的，简洁和繁复都是为了目标的手段而已。","likes_number":1,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1706172873,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":"山东","group_id":0},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]},{"author":{"id":2467716,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/25/a7/84/0e1403ac.jpg","nickname":"圆明居士胤禛","note":"","ucode":"C66DE217C0D604","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":636462,"discussion_content":"简约与繁复都是为内容和读者服务的。实际上，你要看内容与读者之间匹配的程度，如果仅仅面向程序员，你则不需要展开说devops是个什么-点到为止即可，直接给出想给他的关键方案。如果是面向更多人，要满足更多人的好奇心，就要多写一些了。这就是我说的当简则简，当繁则繁。","likes_number":1,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1706172554,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":"山东","group_id":0},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]}]}